00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,400
Science has a clearer story about vaccine myocarditis than social media.

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:08,800
Vaccine myocarditis is rare, especially compared to the risk of COVID-19.

3
00:00:08,800 --> 00:00:13,600
Data shows higher rates in young males, but cases are still infrequent.

4
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:18,400
Studies reveal myocarditis rates are much lower than risks of severe COVID.

5
00:00:18,400 --> 00:00:20,000
Informed choices protect us.

6
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:21,600
Understanding risks empowers us.

7
